description: Follow live text commentary, score updates and match stats from Tranmere Rovers v Fleetwood Town in League Two.
title: Tranmere Rovers 0-0 Fleetwood Town
title_page: Tranmere Rovers 0-0 Fleetwood Town: League Two stats & head-to-head - BBC Sport
maintext:
As Football League clubs, Tranmere have lost all three of their meetings with Fleetwood Town in all competitions, conceding exactly twice in each defeat.
Fleetwood Town’s only previous Football League meeting with Tranmere saw them win 2-1 in November 2019 under Joey Barton.
Tranmere have only lost one of their last six home matches in League Two (W2 D3), although that defeat did come in their most recent one – 1-3 v Colchester earlier this month.
